    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom-quality condition, exhibiting no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior\u2014reflects a legacy of uncompromising care. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly impeccable specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
