    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint swirls, scratches, or stone chips; the body panels are laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, featuring pristine Nappa leather upholstery that retains its original matte finish and scent. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the adaptive driver aids, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete documented service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It sits on original alloy wheels wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Included are both original keys, all owner manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
